    <value>Privacy Policy / Conditions of Use</value>
    <comment>00</comment>
  </data>
  <data name="pageText" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Effective: 07/10/2017&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thank  you for visiting the State of California&amp;rsquo;s Immigrant Guide and reviewing our policy.  Please note, this policy is subject to change  without notice, and reflects the State's current business practices. This policy  is dated July 10, 2017. The State of California also has a privacy policy  available on the &lt;a href="https://www.ca.gov/use/"&gt;CA.gov&lt;/a&gt; website.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 class="h3"&gt;Personal Information&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The State of California is  committed to promoting and protecting the privacy rights of individuals as  enumerated in Article 1 of the California Constitution, the California  Information Practices Act of 1977, and other state and federal laws.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 class="h4"&gt;When it&amp;rsquo;s collected and how it&amp;rsquo;s used&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This website automatically collects  the domain name or Internet Protocol address that relates to the machine used  to access the site, the type of browser and operating system used, the date and  time the website is visited, and the web pages displayed. We do not collect  home addresses, business or e-mail addresses, or account information from  persons who simply browse this Internet website. Electronically collected  personal information is exempt from disclosure under the Public Records Act.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h1 id="conditions"&gt;Conditions of Use&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;h2 class="h3"&gt;Translated Content&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We have used professional third  party translation services to translate some of the English content on this  site into several languages spoken throughout California. Although we have made  every effort to achieve an accurate translation, the California Department of  Technology cannot guarantee complete accuracy. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 class="h3"&gt;Links to other sites&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Our web site has links to websites that might be  useful and/or provide services. Clicking on links to content outside of the  California Immigrant Guide will cause the linked content to open in a new  browser tab or window.  When you click on  links to another site and view content on another site, you are no longer on the  California Immigrant Guide and are subject to the use and privacy policies of  the new site.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 class="h4"&gt;Related services&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;All services promoted on this site are offered by  agencies and departments of the State of California, by contractors with the  State of California, or by organizations that have partnered with the State to  provide the services described.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 class="h4"&gt;State agencies and departments&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Available services vary  between agencies and departments promoted on this site. Each agency and  department within the State of California may have additional privacy and use  policies specific to their mission. We encourage you to review those policies  as you access additional sites within the State of California.&lt;/p&gt;</value>
